data.description: RENO done RIGHT! These owners were especially careful to hand select every detail of this SPACIOUS ONE OWNER HOME when they purchased. They wanted to carry that on and that they did! With UPGRADED countertops, EXCEPTIONAL amounts of cabinet and countertop space in the kitchen plus, an OPEN concept giving a view of the EXPANSIVE living room, dining with beautiful natural light, and complete with NEW WINDOWS throughout, NEW A/C, Luxury vinyl plank in the main areas and ceramic tile in the bathrooms, utility, and entry! Exquisite detail in the living room ceiling with custom wood accents! This home offers a MASSIVE laundry room with MUD SINK, a SPACIOUS OWNERS SUITE with lovely on suite bath, freestanding tub, shower, and a HUGE BACK YARD all right in town- MOMENTS from Fort Johnson. Plus owners are allowing BUYERS to CHOOSE their own APPLIANCES from owners appliance budget!!!
